      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MANEUVER EXPRESS (8) was sent out long odds last time but charged out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 3.5 lengths fourth (29.76) over 520m at this track. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Worth another chance. SPEEDY VAN WEZEL (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (30.43) last time in a Grade 5/6 at Northam. Form at the trip sound including six wins. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Can figure in the finish. LIZZIE LONG LEGS (1) finds it hard to win. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (23.24) at Richmond. Has a good record here at this journey. Can measure up. WINSOME WANDA (5) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
